OL,3,GOPINIONCCould red button provide a more
OL,4,Cinclusive TV experience for BSL viewers
OL,5,
OL,6,FBoth these services can, of course,
OL,7,Fsimply be turned off and on. There is
OL,8,Fno downside or distraction for other
OL,9,Fviewers.
OL,11,FTraditionally sign language
OL,12,Finterpretation has been more
OL,13,Fproblematic.
OL,15,FAround 150,000 people in the UK use
OL,16,FBritish Sign Language. Many of its
OL,17,Fusers have been deaf since birth. BSL
OL,18,Fis a language in its own right.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
