OL,3,GOPINIONCCould red button provide a more
OL,4,Cinclusive TV experience for BSL viewers
OL,5,
OL,6,FBut sign language interpretation can be
OL,7,Fa distraction for the majority of
OL,8,Fviewers, even those who would also
OL,9,Fsupport the principle of making
OL,10,Fprogrammes available to BSL.
OL,12,FThis is the reason BSL programmes are
OL,13,Fusually shown at off peak times or
OL,14,Fovernight to record.
OL,16,FBut is there now a way for the BBC to
OL,17,Fprovide more live BSL? The red button.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
