OL,3,GOPINIONCCould red button provide a more
OL,4,Cinclusive TV experience for BSL viewers
OL,5,
OL,6,FIn recent weeks several programmes `
OL,7,Fnotably Strictly ` have gone out with
OL,8,FBSL interpretation on the BBC's Red
OL,9,FButton service at the same time as the
OL,10,Fmain broadcast on BBC One.
OL,12,FSeveral programmes on Christmas Day and
OL,13,FBoxing Day are being interpreted in
OL,14,Fthis way including Call the Midwife.
OL,16,FSurely this is a better option than the
OL,17,Fovernight Sign Zone?
OL,19,FThis allows BSL users to watch
OL,20,Fprogrammes as they are shown along with
OL,21,Ftheir friends and family.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
