OL,3,GOPINIONCCould red button provide a more
OL,4,Cinclusive TV experience for BSL viewers
OL,5,
OL,6,FThe red button option effectively means
OL,7,Fsign language interpretation becomes an
OL,8,Foptional feature like subtitles and AD.
OL,10,FBBC cuts and changing commissioning
OL,11,Fpriorities mean there is now far less
OL,12,Foriginal red button video content.
OL,14,FAt present the red button video stream
OL,15,Fis mostly being used for endless reruns
OL,16,Fof Fanny Cradock Cooks for Christmas
OL,17,Ffrom 1975.
OL,19,FSurely it would be sensible to turn
OL,20,Fthis stream over so that it be
OL,21,Fprimarily a BSL service?
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
