OL,3,GOPINIONCCould red button provide a more
OL,4,Cinclusive TV experience for BSL viewers
OL,5,
OL,6,FOver time, the need for the overnight
OL,7,FSIgn Zone could be reconsidered.
OL,9,FThe BBC deserves credit for providing
OL,10,FBSL on a wide range of programmes each
OL,11,Fweek. It does not cynically repeat
OL,12,Fprogrammes made years ago to tick
OL,13,Fboxes.
OL,15,FUntil now, Sign Zone and the iPlayer
OL,16,Fwere clearly the best ways of
OL,17,Fdelivering this service.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
