OL,3,GOPINIONCCould red button provide a more
OL,4,Cinclusive TV experience for BSL viewers
OL,5,
OL,6,FBut I really think providing the option
OL,7,Fof BSL on the red button channel at the
OL,8,Fsame time as the main transmission
OL,9,Fshould be the way forward.
OL,11,FThe joy of a channel like BBC One is
OL,12,Fits ability to bring people together.
OL,13,FThose who use BSL should be able to
OL,14,Ffeel welcome too and, via the red
OL,15,Fbutton, enjoy programmes at the same
OL,16,Ftime as the rest of us.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
